latestPosts.caption:
Gratitude for a Successful Makeup Masterclass by Chanchal Sharma

Dear All,

I am delighted to share that yesterday, Chanchal Sharma makeup academy,  successfully hosted an exclusive Makeup Masterclass by celebrity makeup artist Chanchal Sharma at Pacific D21 Mall, Dwarka, Delhi. The event witnessed an enthusiastic participation of 60+ makeup artists from across India, along with several previous and current contestants of Spot’less Face of India.

I extend my heartfelt gratitude to Ms. Chanchal Sharma and her team for inviting me to this remarkable event. It was a privilege to be part of such an enriching and inspiring session.

Looking forward to more such opportunities to elevate the beauty and fashion industry together!

Best Regards,
Tapas Das
📞 9650192813
Model Mentor & Guide
Founder - DCT Model Management & Spot’less Fashion Magazine
Organizer - Spot’less Face of India 2025 (Season 4)
